    echo "  ██╔══╝  ██║╚██╔╝██║██║   ██║██║╚██╔╝██║██║   ██║██║╚██╔╝██║██║   ██║"
    echo "  ███████╗██║ ╚═╝ ██║╚██████╔╝██║ ╚═╝ ██║╚██████╔╝██║ ╚═╝ ██║╚██████╔╝"
    echo "  ╚══════╝╚═╝     ╚═╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═╝     ╚═╝ ╚═════╝ ╚═╝     ╚═╝ ╚═════╝ "
